<div class="min-h-screen pt-24 pb-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-b from-[#ffe2ea] via-[#ffe2ea] via-20% to-[#97DBC1]">
  
  <div class="w-full max-w-md px-4 text-center">
    <div class="bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-sm p-10 md:p-16 rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-none min-h-[400px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">
        パスワードの再設定が<br>完了しました。
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
